{"tid":2219970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實戰線由此始終都係得一條，不過好多人不思進取","createTime":"2020-09-27T09:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T22:18:15.000Z","uid":221035,"like":122,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"e3535e9d202baaac47680421ade374b96eab82eb","tid":2219970,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"咩戰線？奪權！<br />\n<br />\n睇歷史，點樣獨立？你估人地流亡海外真係流亡？<br />\n唔通淨係去英國做收銀等個細路第時有書讀就算？<br />\n去海外嗰啲，人地真係籌集資金、做實業、建軍、做反抗組織、連結外國政治力量<br />\n<br />\n留得係香港嘅，要有啲大志<br />\n黃色經濟圈唔係真係黃色街坊小店圈啊大佬，要有啲生意頭腦發大嚟做，食埋藍絲嘅market<br />\n做生意嘅，諗下點樣擴充多啲唔同地方嘅業務，減少依賴中囯，如果第時獨立咗，個個行業又係同返中囯做生意，就收得皮啦<br />\n<br />\n做咩行業都好，要上位，要有權<br />\n做公務員、醫護、白領，咩都好，一定要爬上去，幾辛苦都要爬上去<br />\n你唔上，第時又係藍絲廢老、老屎忽做管理層，香港就算有民主咪又係食屎<br />\n<br />\n好多嘢，唔好爲做而做，諗清楚目標<br />\n正如文宣，你係諗住動員自己人、感染淺黃變深黃、定係主打淺藍中年人<br />\n所有嘢要有策略要好實際<br />\n革命就係咁，齋講理想，係死好多人兼失敗<br />\n除咗理念，重要有錢、權、勢"},{"pid":"e49e8fb3eecdb1f6770c9f597782c33511bdbaa5","tid":2219970,"uid":221035,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"國安法還國安法<br />\n無力還無力<br />\n<br />\n俾啲大志自己<br />\n努力爬上去"},{"pid":"226455ba5d0e4146975a5d76a2ddc1cd672f74f6","tid":2219970,"uid":221035,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"個個都甘於平凡就永遠都人壓住"},{"pid":"06b56975cfd4df475d7c604ed351fe3e517cab6a","tid":2219970,"uid":289414,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"gay巴出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8351259602e9d046d7a4b64be26a3d5abe3e6c4","tid":2219970,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"又係啲好簡單但冇人做到嘅嘅道理<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1425f46daa0187345d0fb9e3165c69a0100a2034","tid":2219970,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc70353f590e2681b67d329f63055e84226c5c86","tid":2219970,"uid":221035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈如果淨係用嚟俾自己人有「多一個選擇」就死得啦<br />\n<br />\n係要搶market，奪權吖嘛"},{"pid":"e3b259739718ce1a8fed4ed3f8c90c506856b727","tid":2219970,"uid":221035,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"正如有啲話公務員、黨鐵前線係咪黃<br />\n我理得你理啫<br />\n如果你係黃，上到位有權，咪有用囉<br />\n你無權，黃都無用啦"},{"pid":"12f11eb860db742bccc28cf7e3072e933bee5760","tid":2219970,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1fb0e7ad107e7f94639c24b49cd223e770f95529","tid":2219970,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"要擴展影響力，不外乎人脈、錢、權<br />\n想贏想獨立，就一定要諗呢啲<br />\n呢個世界就係咁現實"},{"pid":"1b4d6a64b610d6b78a828be4f6970687b6b7ab8c","tid":2219970,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"其實亂世就一定㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n大家應該睇下有咩機會可以把握<br />\n<br />\n唔係喺度哀嘆香港已死"},{"pid":"083be889fd0588e719e17b5b0abb5576af233edc","tid":2219970,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2ba4ea6c2b5431ad4e8a85c912aa048ab6ea2b","tid":2219970,"uid":20091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729336651df42c21f26b7888b0a01334d71ce9f5","tid":2219970,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{